bubble.text: WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR? GOANIMATE!

ttsdata.text: So you wanna make a cartoon?
But you don't know how to make an cartoon?
GoAnimate! A place where you can make cartoons easily!
There are styles like Comedy World and more!
I will show you how to use it!
First you go on the website GoAnimate.com. Then, click make a video. Then, click a style. Then, start animating!
